20.html|title=GP des Fronti\u00e8res|publisher=Racing Sports Cars|accessdate=20 January 2016}}</ref>\n| style=\"background:#dfdfdf;\"| 2nd\n| Duncan Hamilton\n| [[Jaguar D-Type]]\n|-\n| \n| Coupes des Salon  <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.racingsportscars.com/race/Chimay-1956-05-20-6520.html |title=GP des Fronti\u00e8res 1956 |publisher=Racing Sports Cars |accessdate=9 January 2016}}</ref>\n| style=\"background:#dfdfdf;\"| 2nd\n| Duncan Hamilton\n| [[Jaguar D-Type]]\n|-\n| \n| BRDC Daily Express International Trophy [TC]  <ref>{{cite web|url=http://touringcarracing.net/Races/1956%20Silverstone%20Int.html |title=1956 Silverstone International Trophy |publisher=Touringcarracing.net  |accessdate=9 January 2016}}</ref>\n| style=\"background:#ffdf9f;\"| 3rd\n| [[Jaguar Cars]]\n| [[Jaguar Mark 1|Jaguar 2.4 Litre]]\n|-\n| \n| [[1956 Swedish Grand Prix|Sveriges Grand Prix]] <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.racingsportscars.com/results/Kristianstad-1956-08-12.html|title=Sveriges Grand Prix|publisher=Racing Sports Cars|accessdate=20 January 2016}}</ref>\n| style=\"background:#ffdf9f;\"| 3rd\n| [[Scuderia Ferrari]]\n| [[Ferrari Monza|Ferrari 860 Monza]]\n|-\n| 1957\n| BRDC Daily Express International Trophy [TC]  <ref>{{cite web|url=http://touringcarracing.net/Races/1957%20Silverstone%20Int.html|title=1957 Silverstone International Trophy|publisher=touringcarracing.net|accessdate=20 January 2016}}</ref>\n| style=\"background:#dfdfdf;\"| 2nd\n| [[Jaguar Cars]]\n| [[Jaguar Mark 1|Jaguar 2.4 Litre]]\n|-\n| \n| Aintree International  <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.racingsportscars.com/results/Aintree-1957-07-20.html|title=Aintree International|publisher=Racing Sports Cars|accessdate=20 January 2016}}</ref>\n| style=\"background:#ffdf9f;\"| 3rd\n| \n| [[Jaguar D-Type]]\n|-\n| 1958\n| Whitsun Trophy  <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.racingsportscars.com/results/Goodwood-1958-05-26-12633.html|title=Whitsun Trophy Goodwood|publisher=Racing Sports Cars|accessdate=20 January 2016}}</ref>\n|